Thanks @drpngx for the help. The Jenkins test failure was caused by `//tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test` as the `--update_goldens True` was not run. 

I have rebased and updated the PR with goldens updated. Please take a look and sorry for the inconvenience.
